modules.description: Converts time zone values to and from JSON, and parses string representations into time zone objects. Works with the `Timedesc.Time_zone.t` type, representing time zone information. Used to serialize time zone data for storage or transmission and to validate user input for time zone settings.

Handles date and time parsing, formatting, and arithmetic using custom date and time types. Supports timezone conversions and duration calculations. Enables precise manipulation of calendar dates and clock times in applications requiring temporal logic.

Handles JSON serialization and deserialization of time zone data, converting between string representations and `Timedesc.Time_zone.t` objects. Enables validation of user-provided time zone inputs and ensures consistent storage or transmission of time zone information. Supports parsing ISO 8601 time zone strings and encoding time zones into JSON format. Can be used to store user preferences or exchange time zone data between systems.
